			<a name="1"><font face="verdana" size="3" color="#9f3215"><b>    Erollisi Marr: Blackburrow Raid & Other Events</b></font>
			<br>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			<b><a href="mailto:cromm64@hotmail.com">Arctic Icestorm</a>
			</font><font face="verdana" size="2" color="#9f3215">
			</b></font>[<font face="verdana" size="1" color="black">8/15/2000 3:16:02 PM PST</font>] <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			<b><a href="newsinfo.asp?ID=199511">
			Add Comment
			</a></b></font>
			<br>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black"><Blockquote>
Greetings Young Norrathians!<P>

The Infinite Realm needs your aid!  While off adventuring in Kunark it seems that the foul gnolls of Blackburrow have located and raided our warchests and made off with some loot. We ask you to join us in reclaiming these items and ridding Norrath of this scourge on our society.  <P>

On Saturday August 19th beginning at 3 p.m. EST on the Erollisi Marr server the Infinite Realm is happy to host a raid event for young adventurers in Blackburrow and surroundings.<P>

The gnoll mobs will be equipped with many Fine-Steel weapons and other similar items.  Keep what they drop as our reward for your assistance all while under the buffing and healing protection of the Infinite Realm.<P>

Among the activites:<BR>
A Platinum Lottery<BR>
Languages Taught<BR>
Good-Old Fashioned Killin :)<BR>
and throughout the day we will be hosting many mini-quests with prizes such as a Blood-Stained Tunic, Charred Guardian Shield, Class Quest Armor, A full suit of Blackened-Iron, Bronze Armor, Kunark weapons and many many more....<P>

Hope to see you there....
</blockquote>
